  "body": "<div style=\"display:flex; justify-content:center;\">\n<img src=\"https://github.com/kingnhcomcast/Dirigo/blob/26.1/media/dirigo_banner.png?raw=true\" style=\"height:128px; width:auto;\"/>\n</div>\n\n**Dirigo is a library used in Drahlek's mods.**  \n\n---\n\nProvides a multi-loader abstraction layer to assist in developing mods for Fabric and NeoForge.\n\n## Used By\n\n\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"140\" style=\"min-width:140px;\">\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/cinderstride\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/rZcOAbbe/11b494acecf531275f57bc3e58d9bc5fb74961ab.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\"/>\n</a>\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n\n<strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/cinderstride\">CinderStride</a></strong> – A rare Bastion relic grants Lava Walker boots, letting you walk across lava and turn the Nether’s oceans into your highway.\n\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"140\" style=\"min-width:140px;\">\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/smart-feeding-troughs\">\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/1806/808/64/64/639143175418399232.png\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\"/>\n</a>\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n\n<strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/smart-feeding-troughs\">Smart Feeding Troughs</a></strong> – Automatically feeds and breeds nearby animals in a natural and vanilla-friendly way.\n\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n\n---\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n",
